---
description: GitHub Actions, Docker, and environment secrets
globs: .github/**,Dockerfile,docker-compose*.yml,.dockerignore
alwaysApply: false
---

# CI/CD (`.github/workflows/`)

| Workflow | Trigger | Purpose |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `lint-and-format.yml` | push/PR `main`, `staging` | Node 20, `npm ci`, lint + format:check |
| `tests.yml` | push/PR `main`, `staging` | `npm test` + coverage artifact, job summary |
| `docker-build-and-push.yml` | push `main`, `workflow_dispatch` | Multi-arch push to Docker Hub |

**Docker image:** `${DOCKER_USERNAME}/acquisitions`  
**Secrets:** `DOCKER_USERNAME`, `DOCKER_PASSWORD`  
**Tags:** branch, SHA, `latest`, `prod-YYYYMMDD-HHmmss`  
**Platforms:** `linux/amd64`, `linux/arm64` — Dockerfile `production` target

# Docker local

- **Dev:** `docker-compose.dev.yml` — `neon-local` + app; `npm run docker:dev`
- **Prod:** `docker-compose.prod.yml` — app only, `/health` healthcheck; `npm run docker:prod`
- **Targets:** `development` (full deps), `production` (omit devDeps, non-root)

# Env & git

| Variable | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `DATABASE_URL` | Required |
| `JWT_SECRET` | JWT |
| `ARCJET_KEY` | Arcjet |
| `NEON_LOCAL*` | Local proxy |

**Never commit:** `.env*`, `logs/`, `node_modules/`, `.neon_local/`, `coverage/`  
**Always commit:** `src/`, `tests/`, `drizzle/`, `.github/workflows/`, `.cursor/rules/`
